The article discusses the negative effects of socialism and communism on healthcare and economic policies. It claims that wherever true socialism or communism has been adopted, it has resulted in anguish, devastation, and failure. It argues that under socialist economic policies, Americans can expect their incomes to decrease and their economic freedom to disappear. The article also criticizes the Democrats' "Medicare for All" plan, stating that it would devastate the American healthcare market and result in higher taxes. Finally, it highlights the long history of failure associated with socialist policies worldwide.